Spring 3 has various view resolvers.
> BeanNameViewResolver. 
> InternalResourceViewResolver
> FreeMarkerViewResolver
> ResourceBundleViewResolver (I18n features ) 
> TilesViewResolver
> URLBasedViewResolver
> ContentNegotiatgionViewResolver ( JSP/ XML / JSON )
WE can have multiple viewresolvers in a single application. 
